<img src="http://track.hubspot.com/__ptq.gif?a=25951&k=14&bu=http://www.heimsath.com/blog-0/&r=http://www.heimsath.com/blog-0/bid/90501/Residential-Green-Building-Frequently-Asked-Questions&bvt=rss">

There's lots of talk about green building - but what does it really mean for your project?&nbsp; We've been impressed with many improvements in our industry that have come from the sustainability movement, often referred to as green building.&nbsp; However, not everything that's promoted as green makes sense.&nbsp; Here is the second half of my article on residential green architecture and the frequently asked questions we often encounter -- or download the entire two-part article now:<br>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;<span class="hs-cta-wrapper" id="hs-cta-wrapper-5902614e-67a0-484c-b14f-da6522e3c740">
    <span class="hs-cta-node hs-cta-5902614e-67a0-484c-b14f-da6522e3c740" id="hs-cta-5902614e-67a0-484c-b14f-da6522e3c740">
